      "text": "In planning a covert surveillance operation targeting a suspected fraudster's cash transactions, an investigator must balance investigative necessity against privacy expectations. Which factor is LEAST relevant to determining whether the surveillance plan meets legal and ethical standards under CFE guidelines?",
